query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('amazon-redshift',
'bind',
'carrierwave',
'crashlytics',
'httpurlconnection',
'inputstream',
'java-web-start',
'linux-device-driver',
'openshift',
'oracle-apex',
'paramiko',
'sublimetext',
'wget');
